    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but if we let every group opt out of laws they dont like, doesnt that just lead to chaos? like, if a law is passed to keep people safe or ensure equality, and a group says \"that goes against our beliefs,\" doesnt that pretty much make the law useless for everyone else? it feels like giving them an exemption basically gives them more rights than the rest of us.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
